headline: ArcWest Announces $4 Million Drilling Program at its Todd Creek Copper-Gold Project in 2025, Funded by Freeport-McMoRan Mineral Properties Canada Inc.
summary: Vancouver, British Columbia--(Newsfile Corp. - June 26, 2025) - ArcWest Exploration Inc. (TSXV: AWX) ("ArcWest") is pleased to announce that it has mobilized to begin a drill program at its wholly owned Todd Creek Copper ("Cu") - Gold ("Au)" Project in British Columbia's Golden Triangle, with drilling scheduled to begin by the end of June 2025. Program funding of at least CAD$4 million is being 100% provided by Freeport-McMoRan Mineral Properties Canada Inc. ("Freeport"). ...
